# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Evergreen Cleaning Services — NEVER publish these to GitHub Pages / the live site
# (mirrors the Lawn Care .gitignore)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Apps Script source — contains the live Stripe secret key.
# PASTE-ONLY into the Apps Script editor; it must never be served or committed.
cleaning-apps-script.txt
cleaning-apps-script*.txt
apps-script.txt
apps-script*.txt
*-BACKEND-ADDONS.gs

# Stripe secrets / backup codes
stripe*.txt

# Local databases (not part of the website)
*.db

# Internal multi-agent "operating system" scaffold + all backups (key-bearing)
_Evergreen-OS/

# Editor / manual backups (these embed old copies of the key + SCRIPT_URL)
*.bak
*.bak-*
*.bak.*
*.bak-*.html
*.bak-*.txt
index.html.bak*

# Working notes / internal docs — not for the live site
CHAT_CONTEXT.md
*.md
*.docx
site-audit-report.html

# Raw data export (review before serving)
data.json

# Unused photo staging
Photos/Unused/

# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
_synctest.txt
